        <div class="scard p-6"><div class="check"><div class="check-dot"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg></div><div><strong style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem">15-Year Workmanship Warranty</strong><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.6;margin-top:.25rem">Every Palm Harbor roof installation includes a written 15-year workmanship warranty on top of manufacturer material warranties.</p></div></div></div>
        <div class="scard p-6"><div class="check"><div class="check-dot"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg></div><div><strong style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem">Pinellas County Permits Handled</strong><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.6;margin-top:.25rem">We manage all Pinellas County permit applications and inspections for Palm Harbor roofing projects — no hassle for you.</p></div></div></div>
