      <div class="scard p-8"><div style="width:52px;height:52px;border-radius:14px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;background:rgba(230,168,23,.1);margin-bottom:1rem"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="2"><path d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z"/></svg></div><h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.35rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.75rem">Roof Repair</h3><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7">Leak detection, shingle replacement, tile repair, and flashing restoration for Palm Harbor homes. We diagnose the root cause and fix it right — providing honest assessments without pressure to replace when a repair will suffice.</p></div>
      <div class="scard p-8"><div style="width:52px;height:52px;border-radius:14px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;background:rgba(230,168,23,.1);margin-bottom:1rem"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="2"><path d="M9 21H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h4"/><polyline points="16 17 21 12 16 7"/><line x1="21" y1="12" x2="9" y2="12"/></svg></div><h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.35rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.75rem">Storm Damage & Insurance</h3><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7">After tropical storms and hurricanes, we provide thorough damage assessments for Palm Harbor homeowners, document everything for your insurance claim, and coordinate directly with your adjuster for a smooth claims process.</p></div>
