    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <div class="scard p-8 flex gap-5"><div class="step-num">1</div><div><h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.2rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.5rem">Free Inspection & Estimate</h3><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7">Thorough roof inspection covering decking, underlayment, flashing, and ventilation. You get a detailed written estimate with material options, timelines, and transparent pricing.</p></div></div>
      <div class="scard p-8 flex gap-5"><div class="step-num">2</div><div><h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.2rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.5rem">Material Selection & Permits</h3><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7">Choose your material and color. We pull all Pinellas County permits, order materials from the manufacturer, and schedule a start date that works for your schedule.</p></div></div>
      <div class="scard p-8 flex gap-5"><div class="step-num">3</div><div><h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.2rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.5rem">Professional Installation</h3><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7">Full tear-off, decking inspection and repair, new underlayment and flashing, and roofing system installation to manufacturer specifications. We protect your property throughout.</p></div></div>
      <div class="scard p-8 flex gap-5"><div class="step-num">4</div><div><h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.2rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.5rem">Final Inspection & Warranty</h3><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7">County inspection for code compliance, warranty documentation including our 15-year workmanship warranty, and follow-up at 30 days and 1 year.</p></div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="py-20" style="background:#F7F7F7">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5">
